      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless aesthetic and mechanical integrity that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every surface has been meticulously preserved, reflecting an uncompromising standard of care. We invite serious inquiries for this exceptional specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
