    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car is in truly incredible, pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels just like stepping onto the showroom floor. I\u2019ve meticulously babied it from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, 'like-new' feel without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a museum-grade 2011 BMW M3 (E92), featuring the final naturally aspirated 4.0L S65 V8. This specimen showcases exceptional mechanical preservation, with the high-revving powerplant delivering linear torque and an 8,400 RPM redline through eight individual throttle bodies. The 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, mechanical shifts, complemented by a perfectly functioning M Variable Differential Lock. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing, ensuring peak operational integrity. The chassis remains factory-tight, utilizing its aluminum multi-link suspension and EDC (Electronic Damping Control) to provide unparalleled feedback. The exterior finish is original and flawless, while the interior retains its factory matte texture, free of the typical wear on the bolsters or switchgear. A definitive example for the collector who demands mechanical purity and technical excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2022 model. Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Clean title. No accidents. Maintenance records included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the definition of 'showroom ready.' Every inch of the deep metallic paint glows with a mirror-like finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures it stays pristine. Inside, the premium leather seats remain supple and free of any creases or wear, retaining that new-car aroma. This car has been strictly garage-kept, never seen a winter road, and follows a meticulous maintenance schedule with all service records documented. From the flawless alloy wheels to the crystal-clear infotainment display, there isn't a single blemish or mechanical imperfection to be found. It drives with the precision, quietness, and smoothness of a brand-new machine. If you are looking for a vehicle that has been pampered and preserved to the highest possible standard, this is the one.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle is offered in impeccable condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail since its inception. The exterior finish retains its original showroom luster, complemented by an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Mechanically, the vehicle operates with the precision and reliability expected of a top-tier investment. For the discerning buyer seeking a definitive example of this model, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine asset.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
