      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 Honestly, you have to see this car to believe it. It has been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
