      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a superlative example of BMW\u2019s M-Division engineering. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders with the high-pressure VANOS system and rod bearings meticulously serviced. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip M-differential. The chassis integrity is guaranteed by proactive rear subframe reinforcement, while the suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with upgraded polyurethane bushings. Finished in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent throughout, showing no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. A concours-ready, turn-key machine for the technical purist.",
